  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201507/889aa42c-7dab-4530-9cb7-0e491d05b0bd.jpg\" /></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p785791\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\tFirst though, Frank, a film about a performer who did and didn't exist and a tale about music and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/ambition\" target=\"_blank\">ambition</a> and talent and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fame\" target=\"_blank\">fame</a> and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fragility\" target=\"_blank\">fragility</a>. On the face of it, it's a familiar scenario: <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/suburban\" target=\"_blank\">suburban</a> boy joins <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/eccentric\" target=\"_blank\">eccentric</a> band, goes on the road and is enthralled to the mysterious lead singer. But what's even more enigmatic about the band's presiding <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/genius\" target=\"_blank\">genius</a>, Frank, is that you never see his face. It's hidden beneath a giant, oval <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/papier\" target=\"_blank\">papier</a> mache head, the bright blue eyes <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/perpetually\" target=\"_blank\">perpetually</a> startled. This also means that you might not guess that beneath the mask is actor Michael Fassbender. Fans of Frank Sidebottom, the aspiring musician character created in the 1980s by Chris Sievey, will recognise the face. Sievey kept inside the head and in character at all times on stage and frequently off it. Frank the film draws on the experiences of its co-writer Jon Ronson who was once in the Sidebottom band. But as director Lenny Abrahamson explains, it ranges way beyond memoir.</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t&quot;Somebody ask me a while ago, how did you negotiate the fact fiction divide in this film? I mean, I said, well, we did it by saying, well let's just dump the fact and go totally with the fiction. And that's a great balancer because there's a lot of Frank Sidebottom in this film, but Chris Sievey, he created the original Frank Sidebottom or the Frank Sidebottom was an amazingly, kind of unconventional, playful source of stuff.&quot;&nbsp;</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p785791/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p785791\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795538/\">法国尼斯国庆日遇恐袭 至少80人死亡</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795413/\">BBC把咱们微博上的南海段子都翻成了英文……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795442/\">如何利用BBC动画纠正自己的英式发音？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795464/\">听说鲍里斯被任命外交大臣 外国段子手已开火</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795452/\">特蕾莎梅接任英国首相公开演讲全文 附语言点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795517/\">靠时尚征服英国政坛 英国第2任女首相潮爆了</a></li><li 